nodes.text: A Swokes Swokes caliph, a member of the Congress of Caliphs, was the uncle of a male Swokes Swokes named Choka Chok. When Chok was killed by a Pantoran Jedi named Toro Irana at a restaurant on the Swokes Swokes homeworld of Makem Te, his uncle complained to the New Jedi Order on Yavin 4. The Jedi sent Irana's Jedi Master, the Human Mander Zuma, to investigate the incident.
